def calc_distance(data,center):
    clusters = np.expand_dims(centers, axis=1)
    data = np.expand_dims(data, axis=0)

    eucl = np.linalg.norm(clusters - data, axis=2)

    labels = np.argmin(eucl, axis = 0)
    return labels
In [143]:
def calc_distance_slow(data,center):
    labels = []
    for d in data:
        k_dist = []
        for k in centers:

            eucl = np.linalg.norm(k-d)
            k_dist.append(eucl)

        labels.append(np.argmin(k_dist))

    return np.asarray(labels)

def encode(seq: str):
    pssm = np.zeros((len(seq), 20))
    revmap = {
        val: nr
        for nr, val in enumerate(
            ["A","R","N","D","C","Q","E","G","H","I","L","K","M","F","P","S","T","W","Y","V","X",
            ])}

    for nr, i in enumerate(seq):
        pssm[nr, revmap[i]] = 1  # 0.01

    return pssm

from tqdm.notebook import tqdm
def transform_csv_to_matrix(csv_path:str) -> pd.DataFrame :
    
    df = pd.read_csv(csv_path)
    dms_map = np.zeros((20,len(df.mutated_sequence[0])))
    dms_map[:] = np.NaN
    aa_mapping = {"A":0,"R":1,"N":2,"D":3,"C":4,"Q":5,"E":6,"G":7,"H":8,"I":9,"L":10,"K":11,"M":12,
              "F":13,"P":14,"S":15,"T":16,"W":17,"Y":18,"V":19,}
    seq_l = list(df.iloc[0])

    org_seq = list(seq_l[1])
    org_seq[int(seq_l[0][1:-1])-1] = seq_l[0][0]
    unordered_dicts = df.apply(lambda x: {x[0][1:-1]:{x[0][-1]:x[2]}},axis=1)
    for item in tqdm(unordered_dicts.to_list()):
        pos = (list(item.keys())[0])
        aa,val = (list(item[pos].items())[0])
        dms_map[aa_mapping[aa],int(pos)-1] = val

    for nr,std in enumerate(org_seq):
        dms_map[aa_mapping[std],nr] = 1
    return pd.DataFrame(dms_map,index=aa_mapping.keys(),columns=org_seq)
